DEMAND DRIVEN FORECASTING
-Demand Sensing -> Sensing demand signals related to the market place by market, channel, category and product.
-Demand Shaping -> Using what if analysis, demand planners shape future demand based on tactical and strategic sales/ marketing plans.
-Demand Shifting -> Collaboration with sales, marketing and operations planning to match supply to unconstrained demand.
-Demand Response -> Constrained demand response used to develop a final supply response (plan).
